item.title: About
item.description: Hi! I’m Amanda Yokingco. Welcome to my personal website. I’m so glad you’re here! At the moment, my website is still a work in progress. Nevertheless, I hope you can find what you are looking for. Please check back soon for more updates! Currently, I’m a fourth-year undergraduate student studying Molecular Biology, Biotechnology, and Applied Statistics at the University of Toronto Scarborough. I’m interested in research at the intersections of biology and data science.
